*Triangular de Promoción
*
*As the first level will be extended to 18 teams, it will be played a
*promotion championship in Cartagena between the three best-placed
*professional clubs of the second level afiliated to Dimayor, to select
*the 2 promoted teams to the first level.
*
*[All matches in Cartagena, Pedro de Heredia stadium]

